# Implementation Plan - Handover Report Refinements

This plan focuses on improving the contrast and spacing of the "Handover Report Details" section, enlarging and centering the document header title, and using role initials in the signature grid to ensure a professional, clean, and highly readable document.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> - **Header**: The title "LEAVE APPLICATION FORM" will be **larger** and **centered** at the top of the page.
> - **Signatures**: To prevent overflow and ensure a cleaner fit, I will use **Initials** (1. OM, 2. GM, 3. CEO) in the first column of the signature table.
> - **Contrast**: I will change all 'Handover' labels and text to pure black/near-black.
> - **Spacing**: Padding inside the handover blocks will be increased.

